    <hr />

    <h2 id="why-xp-exists">Why XPGuess Uses XP</h2>
    <p>
      XP exists to solve a real educational gap: many people interact with sports outcomes without understanding how decisions are actually made.
      XP helps learners track progress without introducing monetization pressure.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Encourages structured learning and consistency</li>
      <li>Tracks engagement over time</li>
      <li>Supports youth-safe, education-first participation</li>
      <li>Creates transparent milestones for coaches, parents, and learners</li>
    </ul>

